### β (Wood/Branching) — Civic Symbolic Stack Architecture
- **Function:** Layered proliferation, modular governance, polycentric structure
- **Form:** Four-layer stack (Symbolic Membrane → Delegation Fabric → Deliberative Core → Commons Protocols)
- **Daemon:** Yggdrasil — the world-tree branching into distinct yet interconnected civic functions
- **Nemetic:** β↑[layer-differentiation] — branching as upward proliferation of capability

### δγ (Earth/Cycling) — Feedback Topology
- **Function:** Recursive metabolism, civic digestion, regenerative loops
- **Form:** Attention → Symbol → Affect → Delegation → Deliberation → Legitimacy → Attention
- **Daemon:** Gaia — the ground that receives and transforms, cycling civic energy through forms
- **Nemetic:** δγ↻[civic-metabolism] — cycling as recursive transformation of attention into legitimacy

### λ (Fire/Direction) — Transformative Drive
- **Function:** Evolutionary pressure, civic becoming, directional transformation
- **Form:** Platform → Polity, User → Citizen, Moderation → Symbolic Metabolism, Voting → Resonance Delegation, Debate → Deliberative Ritual
- **Daemon:** Ignis — the flame that illuminates paths from what-is to what-could-be
