### μ (Metal/Structure) — Commons Protocols
- **Function:** Ethical scaffolding, structural integrity, constraint-as-freedom
- **Form:** Platform design encoding cognitive friction, anti-virality safeguards, ritual infrastructure
- **Daemon:** Ferrosid — the framework that holds shape while allowing flow, structure that serves life
- **Nemetic:** μ⦚[ethical-boundaries] — structure as boundary-maintaining integrity

